{"title":"革命烈士诗钞","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命烈士诗钞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓中夏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那有斩不除的荆棘？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那有打不死的豺虎？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那有推不翻的山岳？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你只须奋斗着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛勇的奋斗着；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"持续着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远的持续着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利就是你的了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利就是你的了！受　审　方志敏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人只能砍下我们的头颅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不能动摇我们的信仰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我们信仰的主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乃是宇宙的真理！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为着共产主义牺牲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为着苏维埃流血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是我们十分情愿的啊！让"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死的死去吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殷　夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让死的死去吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的血并不白流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们含笑的躺在路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛还诚恳地向我们点头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的血画成地图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染红了多少农村，城头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们光荣地死去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不能向他们把泪流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人在瞄准了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要举起我们的手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让死的死去吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的血并不白流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不要悲哀或叹息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫漫的长途横在前头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走去吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争中消息不要走漏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们尽了责任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们还要抖擞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"囚　歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶　挺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人进出的门紧锁着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为狗爬出的洞敞开着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个声音高叫着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——爬出来呵，给尔自由！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我渴望着自由，但也深知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人的躯体那能由狗的洞子爬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只期待着，那一天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下的火冲腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把这活棺材和我一齐烧掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我应该在烈火和热血中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得到永生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"答敌人审问"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘绍南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大丈夫，要革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立志创造新社会；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为工农，谋幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百折不挠气不馁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们杀了我一人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像明灯暂被狂风吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命少了我一人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比大海丢了一滴水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命声势如浪涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起一伏前后追，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪打沙埋众贼子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕妖魔逞凶威。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白旗倒了红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老子生死在这回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走上前来不下跪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贼子们，睁开眼睛看爷爷！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}